column5: Son gets home from work and says "Lets go. We got 3 hours daylight left". Time to hit another spot now that the water has warmed a touch. Also an opportunity to test a couple more colour patterns. Had us a nice evening with lots of crappie and bull gills to keep us entertained.     Life is good.
Some good eats right there!  Where is the customary sink shot?  G
Nice stuff. Wish I fared out as good. Do you keep them for eating?
I would love to find a place around here for some bull gills like that!  Nice going!
very sweet. nice to see all that after this past winter
Good start to the warm weather season!
You've got the pannies dialed in.  Enjoy your crappie breakie
Very nice! I need to get my son out soon for some panfish.
Way to go Bruce!,nice feed there .
Those are some nice looking fish!
